<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-13770] Properties of class Map does not work with Spring Boot 2.x</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-13770</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From version 2.22.0 onwards spring-boot version is upgraded to 2.x&lt;br/&gt;
After that all Map properties are not working&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example in application.properties&lt;br/&gt;
camel.component.salesforce.http-client-properties is treated as string instead of Map and whatever value we provide to it, the Map is initialize as null&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
